                <div class="aboutGameSection">
                    <h1>Does it worth your time?</h1>
                    <p>Vampyr is a story rich, dialog heavy game, where choices matter. You spend most of your playtime    
                        talking with NPCs and the choices you have to make will affect not only their fate but also the
                        main story. These, combined with the fact that there is no manual save feature, will force you
                        to pay attention to the dialogs. The combat will get repetitive but not necessarily boring. Both
                        crafting and leveling systems are simple enough, leaving you to enjoy the atmosphere, the
                        environment and the story.</p>
                    <h2>First Playthrough</h2>
                    <p>To get most of the experience the game has to offer, for your first playthrough do not kill any
                        citizens. You aim for 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[3].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[3].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[3].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>,
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[11].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[11].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[11].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>, 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[21].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[21].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[21].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. Other achievements you can unlock are 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[4].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[4].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[4].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>, 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[14].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[14].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[14].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[12].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[12].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[12].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. Do not worry about collectibes, since you cannot find them all on this playthrough 
                        and lastly, all story achievements will unlock no matter the ending.
                    </p>
                    <h2>Second Playthrough</h2>
                    <p>For this playthrough you need to find all the collectibes, turn all districts to hostile status
                        and unlock 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[5].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[5].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[5].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. Finding all collectibes
                        will unlock 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[6].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[6].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[6].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>, 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[7].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[7].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[7].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>, 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[8].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[8].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[8].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>, 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[10].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[10].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[10].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[9].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[9].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[9].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. The achievements for killing everyone are
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[2].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[2].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[2].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>, 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[19].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[19].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[19].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span> and 
                        <span class="achievement"><%= achievements[27].displayName %>                                
                            <span class="tooltip-content"><img src= <%= achievements[27].icon %> >
                                <span class="tooltip-text"><%= achievements[27].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>. You do not need to finish the game a second time to unlock all of the achievements.
                    </p>
                    <h3>Time Saving Resources</h3>
                    <p><a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1409469713" target="_blank">100%
                            Achievement Guide (by THN)</a> - Very well organised.<br>
                        <a href="https://www.neoseeker.com/vampyr/walkthrough" target="_blank">Vampyr Walkthrough and
                            Guide</a> - Contains detailed information about the characters, the dialog choices and their
                        consequences, amongst other things.<br>
                        <a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/vampyr/mods/15" target="_blank">Save Tool</a> - Gives you the
                        ability to manually save the game.
                    </p>
